  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of High-dose Leukocytapheresis Using a Large Filter in Refractory Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Efficacy of High-dose Leukocytapheresis Using a Large Filter in Patients With Refractory Asthma</official_title>
